{"tid":1793660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新職業 恥笑師","createTime":"2019-12-22T14:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:17:40.000Z","uid":266591,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36f3a1679d1abce5866f1346a4dee718f6ebe5bb","tid":1793660,"uid":266591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"對付狗 新職業 恥笑師<br />\n望住d狗 淨係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">笑</span></span></strong><br />\n最緊要大大力望住佢地笑<br />\n用最賤最mean既樣笑<br />\n大大聲 仲要人多<br />\n粗口都唔使<br />\n <strong>唔使有內容</strong><br />\n近笑又得 離遠笑又得<br />\n<br />\n你諗下 全部狗都係自尊心薄弱既狗<br />\n佢既狗生 根本就係垃圾<br />\n由細到大 書又讀唔成<br />\n成世葡萄人<br />\n睇住隔離拉讚陳太個仔<br />\n人地問返佢阿媽 ：你個仔做咩架？<br />\n佢阿媽根本就唔想答人<br />\n今時今日佢地可以威可以做錯事都有佢阿頭讚 有2皮幾野人工 覺得高過d office工<br />\n緊係開心喇~~~<br />\n<br />\n對住佢地笑<br />\n自卑既垃圾自然會觸痛到佢地內心既弱點<br />\n由內至外崩潰<br />\n<br />\n對付<strong>臥底狗</strong>望住佢 圍住佢笑 <br />\n唔使理論既<br />\n大大力<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">恥笑</span></span></strong></span>就得<br />\n戰音都無晒<br />\n祝<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">笑運亨通</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2b32448c6896029293d32495d2df94f47ef13162","tid":1793660,"uid":266591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d05a9f5404e9c499958982636b37f49b2c25812","tid":1793660,"uid":266591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"新職業解鎖了"},{"pid":"092c06e72f257da5ed35c5d7f68291ed974b48ad","tid":1793660,"uid":323107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"笑撚柒班做狗嘅"},{"pid":"22c0ff5dba330fe31e70c44c0a61a42c65a6f3f3","tid":1793660,"uid":266591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"大大力"},{"pid":"7702ddaf8be3beaca12f768cf68a1f91bd2baf0a","tid":1793660,"uid":266591,"like":0